 [VRChat] 鸟取县仓吉市官方元宇宙“虚拟仓吉”ver1.0开放，七新久VTuber的旅行视频也将公开https://www.moguravr.com/vrchat-kurayoshi-ver1-0/ノンジャンル人生 Fri, 01 Mar 2024 07:19:38 +0000 VRChatVTuberメタバースななしいんく倉吉 https://www.moguravr.com/?p=246971 <p>鸟取县仓吉市的官方元宇宙“虚拟仓吉”ver1.0已在VRChat上开放。 “虚拟仓吉”是鸟取县仓吉市Mogura株式会社创建的“仓吉仓吉项目”中的虚拟仓吉事业。</p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/vrchat-kurayoshi-ver1-0/">[VRChat]鸟取县仓吉市官方元宇宙“虚拟仓吉”ver1.0已开放。Nanashinku VTuber的旅行视频也将公开。</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a> 。</p> ; <p><a href="https://www.city.kurayoshi.lg.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">鸟取县仓吉市</a>的官方元宇宙<strong>“虚拟仓吉”ver1.0</strong>已在<a href="https://hello.vrchat.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VRChat</a>上开放。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.850idj6olc41-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.850idj6olc41-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.850idj6olc41-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.850idj6olc41-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.850idj6olc41-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> “虚拟仓吉”是<a href="https://mogura.co/ja/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mogura株式会社</a>与鸟取县仓吉市以及<a href="https://www.odakyu.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">小田急电铁株式会社</a>合作开发的<a href="https://www.city.kurayoshi.lg.jp/gyousei/pressrelease/m458/p159-1/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“仓吉仓吉项目”中虚拟仓吉项目</a>的一部分。 <a href="https://gugenka.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Gugenka</a>负责世界上的一些生产。以3D方式再现仓吉市的街景、观光景点、特产等，让您在虚拟体验中了解仓吉的魅力。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/97f6dc900daf500208d6f84afd70da90-kix.o15fxx6ksz1c-jpg.webp" targ