e_official_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VEE</a> ”已开始销售其虚拟艺人<a href="https://twitter.com/hiyohiyovee" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chihiyo Hiyori</a>的生日商品和声音。</p><p>商品包括亚克力立体模型支架和使用插画家 Pan-san 绘制的插图的锡制徽章（2 件套），这次除了套装销售外，还将单独出售商品。</p><p>另外，作为购买套装的特典，还附赠了一张写有日和千日代亲笔留言的明信片。</p><p><a href="https://shop.vee-official.jp/s/ve01/?ima=2643" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击此处</a>了解销售地点。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000106.000049041.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">索尼音乐娱乐公司新闻稿</a></p><h2>《Vebop Project》第二代试镜举行</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/98c20c0c1f3ea2871b9d9da81acde282-kix.q8gfc6jfkwww-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/98c20c0c1f3ea2871b9d9da81acde282-kix.q8gfc6jfkwww-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/98c20c0c1f3ea2871b9d9da81acde282-kix.q8gfc6jfkwww-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/98c20c0c1f3ea2871b9d9da81acde282-kix.q8gfc6jfkwww-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/98c20c0c1f3ea2871b9d9da81acde282-kix.q8gfc6jfkwww-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/98c20c0c1f3ea2871b9d9da81acde282-kix.q8gfc6jfkwww-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/98c20c0c1f3ea2871b9d9da81acde282-kix.q8gfc6jfkwww-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://twitter.com/REALITY_Studio_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">REALITY Studios Inc.</a>正在为VTuber经纪公司“ <a href="https://twitter.com/Vebop_Project" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vebop Project</a> ”举办第二代人才选拔。招募时间为3月1日（星期五）0:00至3月31日（星期日）23:59。</p><p>成功的人才将获得对其活​​动的全面支持，包括提供其活动所需的角色设计和Live2D模型，以及借用一些发行活动所需的设备。</p><p>单击<a href="https://vebop.net/audition/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>申请试镜。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000347.000021973.html" target=